Package entities

Class ProjectApplication

java.lang.Object
entities.ProjectApplication
public class ProjectApplication extends Object
Represents an application for a housing project by an applicant. The application holds details such as the applicant's NRIC, marital status, age, project details, and booking status.

    • ProjectApplication

      public ProjectApplication(String nric, String maritalStatus, int age, String projectName, String flatType)
      Creates a new ProjectApplication for an applicant with the given details. The application status is set to "Pending" and flatBooking is set to false by default.
      Parameters:
      nric - The NRIC of the applicant
      maritalStatus - The marital status of the applicant
      age - The age of the applicant
      projectName - The name of the project
      flatType - The type of flat applied for

    • ProjectApplication

      maritalStatus - The marital status of the applicant
      age - The age of the applicant
      applicationStatus - The current status of the application
      projectName - The name of the project
      flatType - The type of flat applied for
      flatBooked - Whether the flat has been booked or not
